sentence: show me first class flights from: new york to miami leaving on a tuesday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.day_name||'"', '"'||v6.flight_id||'"', '"'||v7.fare_id||'"',
 '"'||v8.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v8.class_type||'"',
 '"'||v9.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v10.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v10.day_name||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, days v5, flight_fare v6,
 fare v7, fare_basis v8, fare_basis v9, days v10 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) 
AND (v5.day_name = 'TUESDAY')) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v6.flight_id) AND ((v6.fare_id = ANY v7.fare_id) 
AND (((v7.fare_basis_code = ANY v8.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v8.class_type = 'FIRST')) AND ((v7.fare_basis_code = ANY v9.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v9.basis_days = ANY v10.days_code) 
AND (v10.day_name = 'TUESDAY')))))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MIAMI ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE . FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE ( FARE.FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS.FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS.CLASS_TYPE = ' FIRST ' ) AND FARE . FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS . FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS . BASIS_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
